=head1 DESCRIPTION

Includes information about tags you define to assign tagged resources
to a backup plan.

Include the prefix C<aws:ResourceTag> in your tags. For example,
C<"aws:ResourceTag/TagKey1": "Value1">.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ConditionKey => Str

The key in a key-value pair. For example, in the tag C<Department:
Accounting>, C<Department> is the key.


=head2 ConditionValue => Str

The value in a key-value pair. For example, in the tag C<Department:
Accounting>, C<Accounting> is the value.



